Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Marito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All units, scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he uses lightning for both \Ndefense and offense,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there might be an opening \N{\alpha&HFF&}...{\r}when he switches between them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it'll be more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are our options?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Marito!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Message from the Deucalion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,HQ is ordering us to pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dales Platoon and Orlov Platoon \Nshould have gotten the same order.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Except what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back! Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dales 22!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The invisible Cataphract we \Ncouldn't destroy is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Clydesdale Leader to Orlov Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Orlov Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the last one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A lightning one,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an invisible one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a third one too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them to carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Surround and annihilate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Asseylum!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done all I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is pray now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
