Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dales 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Clydesdale Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaizuka Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The smokescreen should give us a degree of cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can also use the smoke to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,On your right! Evade fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening, Kaizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were gonna keep the lightning one busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It suddenly shifted its attention to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we surrounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Deucalion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage report!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're discharging it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the ship down and extract all our Cataphracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,On the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the ship down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,KCAS, ten knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going down too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the tail wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Aldnoah Drive can handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Send all power to the antigravity device!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Vertical speed to 1,200 feet per second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the ship!{chopper}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab Dales Platoon and hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the bow doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrieve all our Cataphracts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy Cataphract is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire the main guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All Cataphracts extracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Cataphract on our stern!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Same type as the one we destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Another at two o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't be reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve enemy contacts... Sixteen... Twenty-four...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it replicate itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Full ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Weather radar, Doppler radar, both offline!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The invisible bastard must have damaged our discharge equipment{} with his attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All comm links are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,GPS link lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,2D radar is dead too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep ascending!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So I could convince you of the wisdom of following Count Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall let him know at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing I would ask of you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Might I be granted an audience with Princess Asseylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,An audience with Her Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And if possible, with Count Troyard as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't as easy as it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I shall attempt to see your wish accommodated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be indebted to me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose the saying goes that defeat makes you stronger, but you're exemplary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You are attempting to be on good terms not only with Count Troyard but also with Princess Asseylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,However, don't make your ambitions so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone might exploit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Asseylum is an impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare a shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting the enemy escape is hardly cause for congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We did, however, accomplish our primary objective of securing territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A fine victory, I would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt the ranks of those loyal to you will swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is less reliable than a knight's pledge of fealty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how should I answer \NCount Barouhcruz's request?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him have his wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mazuurek, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He can meet the princess if he so desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She will be only too happy to help us grow in power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't something we can fix with duct tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Night vision's out as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can't even fly by eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What isn't working? The sensors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that, Lieutenant Kaizuka?{what}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be much else. \NThe ship has been meandering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to imagine there could be \Nany defects in the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Enough of that! Just help us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's going wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest lowering our altitude somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fly low enough, enemy radar won't detect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too nervous to go any lower with the altimeter and GPWS both dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can determine how high we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're currently at 9,200.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you also pick up VOR stations?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When you can read both signals, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll calculate our radial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's our heading? I was trying to put us on 110.{calling the police cuz this show is so bad}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty much on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Offset yourself by three degrees for \Ntwo minutes, and then straighten out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. Are we caught in some nasty turbulence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it's a long patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case, slow—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is easy. I've done it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess experience will be the most important thing from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I catch an LLG, I'll let you know.{what even is this}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we should be thanking you for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Marito was surprised you'd do something so crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him he's the last person who can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So the preparations for the founding are proceeding smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A new kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can visit your homeworld, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a planet of apes, not men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be where I am from, but it is hardly home—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,or rather, I suppose I never had a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the same in that regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither Vers nor my noble rank offer me any peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere I may be together with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,more than anywhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You honor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall return later, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Slaine. I've had dinner prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I still have many pressing matters to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaho—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, you really helped Nina yesterday. She was super happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you make of the enemy's coordinated attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're simply so backed into a corner that they're forced to throw away their pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then we probably have nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think it has something \Nto do with the announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That Orbital Knight named Slaine Troyard who's always lurking behind Princess Asseylum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's even beaten Kaizuka Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If everything that's happened is part of that boy's plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,then this isn't something we \Ncan win with numbers alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Matsuribi, sir and madams.{we're using AF ranks for the rest so this seems like the best compromise}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message from HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A request for reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Launch an all-out attack \Nto reclaim our captured territory."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're throwing sheer numbers at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the long and short of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And how have you fared since?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Physically, I feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,However, my memory is still rather hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is hardly surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The very fact that you regained consciousness was nothing short of a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not force yourself to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Slaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I must take my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall return. Please look after Her Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Sir Slaine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can guess what you wish to ask about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The proclamation, yes? Taking me as her husband \Nand founding a new kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That proclamation issued by Princess Lemrina
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,was born from the weakness in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to hold on to my faith that Princess Asseylum would awaken some day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I suppose I must have given up \Nsomewhere deep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But then a miracle took place, \Nas if to reprimand me for being such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With the situation having changed so drastically,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the one thing I must focus on now \Nis how I can make Her Highness happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can spare a thought for nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But what of Princess Lemrina?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what she is looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:16:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She likely seeks the same thing I do—\Na place where she can find solace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is something that \Nneither of us will ever obtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot tell her everything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be that she hates herself \Nfor what she's doing right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but that does not concern me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I had waited with such hope \Nfor Her Highness to awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, my greatest hope \Nis that her memory never returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am overjoyed to see your newfound resolve to serve my trusted Count Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness is too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fully prepared to serve both Your Highness \Nand Count Troyard with wholehearted devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I too was touched by Count Mazuurek's drive
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:17:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,as he swore to rise up once again for the sake of Vers' future
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,even as he was held prisoner on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Begging Your Highness' pardon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am given to understand that you once underwent similar hardships on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, one could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrans are all... so vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no one that Your Highness grew close to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to? I think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I left all interaction with Terrans to my handmaiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I once entertained the notion \Nof reconciling with those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I see what a fool I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Slaine not here now, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Slaine has been preoccupied with preparations for the new operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He said as much earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been locking himself \Nin his castle far too often lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever he is doing, \Ncan he not do it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am told that precious resources are involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go over to the Landing Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you unharmed, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, how long will it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall see you to your room, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pardon the delay, Count Mazuurek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you to the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finished checking my credentials, I take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for our discourtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. The fault is entirely mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in quite the predicament when my ship broke down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How fortunate for me that \Nyou should be in the vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see... Count Troyard is still at the moon base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I regret to say that you have missed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Harklight is on his way as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made my move as soon as I was certain that he would not be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Troyard is traveling between here and the moon base more than he should need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That makes it clear where Her Highness must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these Terran flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This castle has undergone quite the transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was an acquaintance of its former lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He detested all things Terran, \Nfearing that they harbored microorganisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers on Earth are perfectly safe—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have been to Earth, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No. I'm simply relaying what I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Princess Asseylum had an attendant, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Her Highness went to Earth without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't referring to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I must be going!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly have not been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of what took place on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about a boy named Kaizuka Inaho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will it be before you \Nrelease your grip on his feelings?{being lemrina is suffering}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He said that he wanted me to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To the princess who knew about Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This amulet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
